Steps to do a release (automate eventually):

Tag
===

- tag in svn
- switch to tag
- update version number:
    setup.py
    src/mode.py
    doc/tex/Makefile
    doc/tex/mode.tex
- update date in doc/tex/mode.tex
- checkin tag


Distribute
==========

- export tag to www.zetadev.com/software/mode.py/<version>
- generate docs
    cd docs/tex && make all
- build packages into dist/
    make pkg


Announce
========

- update http://zetadev.com/software/mode.py/
- announce on ...
    nntp://comp.lang.python.announce
    http://tech.whit537.org/
